news.title: Jammu & Kashmir government identifies 625 acres of land for industrial estates

news.title: Madhya Pradesh's 2025-26 budget prioritizes urban development with major allocations
news.para: Urban transformation programmes receive notable attention, with Rs 1,071 crore allocated to AMRUT 2.0 and Rs 1,000 crore to Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana (Urban) 2.0 BLC.

news.title: Bihar government extends deadline for land survey till December 2026
